{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Anomaly Zero:Twelve</strong> is a slow-paced horror game where your awareness and attention to details will prevail! Scan your surroundings in every loop and find &quot;anomalies&quot;. An &quot;anomaly&quot; can be a subtle unsettling change, or a major threat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Follow these simple rules, and you should manage to make it out alive:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Did you notice something <u>odd, scary</u>? HEAD BACK TO THE <u>FRONT DOOR</u>!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Nothing is out of place? GO TO THE BALCONY, THROUGH THE <u>GLASS DOOR</u>!</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A correct decision is a <u>1-minute</u> step forward, BUT BE CAREFUL every wrong decision will bring you back <u>3-minutes</u> in the past!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440320/extras/libhero.png?t=1738611272\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>[Controls]</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Move with WASD / ZQSD (<strong>GAMEPAD</strong>: Left / Right Joysticks)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mouse Left Click to interact (<strong>GAMEPAD</strong>: A Button)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mouse Right Click to zoom in (<strong>GAMEPAD</strong>: X Button)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shift / Ctrl / C to crouch (<strong>GAMEPAD</strong>: B Button)</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440320/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738611272","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440320/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738611272","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3440320